Package: dsmSearch
Type: Package
Title: DSM and LiDAR downloader
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Xiaohao", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "xiaohaoy@umich.edu"),
           person("Nathan", "Fox", role = c("aut")),
           person("Derek", "Van Berkel", role = c("aut")),
           person("Mark", "Lindquist", role = c("aut")))
Description: A collection of functions to search and donwload 
    DSM (Digital Surface Model) and LiDAR (Light Detection and Ranging) data via APIs, 
    including OpenTopography API <https://portal.opentopography.org/apidocs/> and 
    TNMAccess API <https://tnmaccess.nationalmap.gov/api/v1/docs>.
